(b)~Band diagram of eigenmode dispersion: grey shading highlights the band gap, and the split band-edge modes marked by cyan open circles.

The geometry parameters are $l$=$500$nm, $w$=$500$nm, $wa$=$1500$nm, $la$=$250$nm, $r$=$150$nm, and the height of the structure is $h$=$220$nm.
}
